:"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":41197,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/09\/19\/umar-on-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":34086,"position":2},"title":"Umar on Abu Bakr: He was our master, the best of us","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 19, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \"Abu Bakr was the most beloved of us to the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, as he was the best of us and our master.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 7407 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6819,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/21\/umar-competes-with-abu-bakr\/","url_meta":{"origin":34086,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Competition: Umar tries to compete with Abu Bakr","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 21, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar ibn al-Khattab reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, ordered us to give charity and at the time I had some wealth. I said to myself, \u201cToday I will outdo Abu Bakr, if ever there were a day to outdo him.\u201d I went with half\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.co